About the game: You really want to know more? Ok, alright, fine. It's a story where you play as a guy who goes to a psychologist to deal with his problems. But then suddenly, out of nowhere, completely unexpectedly... very interesting things happen and adventure begins! Gameplay mostly includes decision making and riddles. It's a visual novel after all, so what do you expect? Action gameplay? Maybe a little bit. That's all. Thank you and have a good day. Yeah, I can into gifs.
